oper tool for confirming connection to said API.","version":"0.1","description":"Call the API installation and receive a response of 'ECHO'. Developer tool for confirming connection to said API.","author":"Vince Wooll","authoremail":"sales@jomres.net","lastupdate":"2016\/12\/16","min_jomres_ver":"9.8.21","manual_link":"","change_log":"","highlight":"","image":"","demo_url":""},"api_feature_email":{"name":"api_feature_email","category":"REST API","marketing":"Functionality that allows API Clients to retrieve your email address","version":"0.4","description":"Experimental plugin. Functionality that allows API Clients to retrieve your email address","author":"Vince Wooll","authoremail":"sales@jomres.net","lastupdate":"2016\/10\/25","min_jomres_ver":"9.8.15","manual_link":"","change_log":"v0.3 Modified how data is returned. v0.4 Added SET NAMES UTF8","highlight":"","image":"https:\/\/www.jomres.net\/manual\/images\/Manual\/09_38_zsbjx.png","demo_url":""},"api_feature_favourites":{"name":"api_feature_favourites","category":"REST API","marketing":"Functionality that allows editing of user's favourites through the API","version":"0.4","description":"Experimental plugin. Functionality that allows editing of user's favourites through the API","author":"Vince Wooll","authoremail":"sales@jomres.net","lastupdate":"2016\/10\/25","min_jomres_ver":"9.8.15","manual_link":"","change_log":"v0.3 Modified how data is returned. v0.4 Added SET NAMES UTF8","highlight":"","image":"https:\/\/www.jomres.net\/manual\/images\/Manual\/09_38_6dfbu.png","demo_url":""},"api_feature_guests":{"name":"api_feature_guests","category":"REST API","marketing":"Functionality that allows listing and modification of guests through the API","version":"1.0","description":"Experimental plugin. Functionality that allows listing and modification of guests through the API","author":"","authoremail":"","lastupdate":"2018\/04\/18","min_jomres_ver":"9.11.0","manual_link":"","change_log":"1.0  Plugin updated to work with Jomres data encryption of user details.","highlight":"","image":"","demo_url":""},"api_feature_guesttypes":{"name":"api_feature_guesttypes","category":"REST API","marketing":"Functionality that allows view and modify of guest types through the API","version":"1.3","description":"Functionality that allows view and modify of guest types through the API","author":"","authoremail":"","lastupdate":"2017\/05\/08","min_jomres_ver":"9.8.30","manual_link":"","change_log":"v1.2 Plugin updated to harden some inputs. v1.3 Plugin updated to add ID of newly created guest types.","highlight":"","image":"","demo_url":""},"api_feature_lastactive":{"name":"api_feature_lastactive","category":"REST API","marketing":"Functionality that allows view last active through the API","version":"0.1","description":"Experimental plugin. Functionality that allows view last active through the API","author":"","authoremail":"","lastupdate":"2017\/01\/03","min_jomres_ver":"9.8.26","manual_link":"","change_log":"","highlight":"","image":"","demo_url":""},"api_feature_listbooking":{"name":"api_feature_listbooking","category":"REST API","marketing":"Functionality that allows view of list booking through the API","version":"1.0","description":"Experimental plugin. Functionality that allows view of list booking through the API","author":"","authoremail":"","lastupdate":"2018\/04\/18","min_jomres_ver":"9.11.0","manual_link":"","change_log":"v0.2 Updated notes and tidied up code a little. v1.0 Plugin updated to work with Jomres data encryption of user details.","highlight":"","image":"","demo_url":""},"api_feature_listinvoices":{"name":"api_feature_listinvoices","category":"REST API","marketing":"Functionality that allows view of list invoices through the API","version":"1.0","description":"Experimental plugin. Functionality that allows view of list invoices through the API","author":"","authoremail":"","lastupdate":"2018\/04\/18","min_jomres_ver":"9.11.0","manual_link":"","change_log":"v0.2 Fixed a security hole that would allow a manager to view any invoice on the site, not just their own invoices. Significant rewrite of sections of code to remove code that is not required\/redundant and clarify responses. Notes updated. 1.0 Plugin updated to work with Jomres data encryption of user details.","highlight":"","image":"","demo_url":""},"api_feature_overview":{"name":"api_feature_overview","category":"REST API","marketing":"Functionality that allows editing of overview plugin through the API","version":"1.0","description":"Functionality that allows editing of overview plugin through the API","author":"","authoremail":"","lastupdate":"2018\/04\/18","min_jomres_ver":"9.11.0","manual_link":"","change_log":"v0.2 Removed redundant code and updated notes. v1.0 Plugin updated to work with Jomres data encryption of user details.","highlight":"","image":"","demo_url":""},"api_feature_properties":{"name":"api_feature_properties","category":"REST API","marketing":"Functionality that allows editing of manager's properties through the API","version":"0.8","description":"Functionality that allows editing of manager's properties through the API","author":"Vince Wooll","authoremail":"sales@jomres.net","lastupdate":"2018\/03\/14","min_jomres_ver":"9.10.0","manual_link":"","change_log":"v0.3 Modified how data is returned. v0.4 Added SET NAMES UTF8 v0.5 added room type images. v0.6 Fixed an issue caused by user profile changes when getting list of all property uids. v0.7 Removed endpoints that should exist in Site Structure. v0.8 Adjustment to remove Jomres version from its old setting. ","highlight":"","image":"https:\/\/www.jomres.net\/manual\/images\/Manual\/09_39_3x5p6.png","demo_url":""},"api_feature_search":{"name":"api_feature_search","category":"REST API","marketing":"Functionality that allows API Clients to search for properties.","version":"0.5","description":"Functionality that allows API Clients to search the database. Requires installation of ajax search composite plugin to function.","author":"Vince Wooll","authoremail":"sales@jomres.net","lastupdate":"2017\/07\/02","min_jomres_ver":"9.9.5","manual_link":"","change_log":"v0.3 Modified how data is returned. v0.4 Removed endpoints that should be in Site Structure plugin. 0.5 Added support for auth_free functionality (available v9.9.6 of Jomres), meaning that anybody can access this part of the api, you do not need a client id\/secret pair.","highlight":"","image":"","demo_url":""},"api_feature_site_structure":{"name":"api_feature_site_structure","category":"REST API","marketing":"Functionality that allows API Clients to retrieve information about the site structure.","version":"0.3","description":"Functionality that allows API Clients to retrieve information about the site structure. As this information is not property specific there is no requirements for scope validation, therefore so long as the client themselves (the Oauth key pair ) has been validated then they can pull the information out of the system.","author":"Vince Wooll","authoremail":"sales@jomres.net","lastupdate":"2017\/05\/12","min_jomres_ver":"9.8.30","manual_link":"","change_log":"v0.2 Modified how region names are determined v0.3 Modified how country names are determined.","highlight":"","image":"","demo_url":""},"api_feature_superserver":{"name":"api_feature_superserver","marketing":"Allows the superserver to query the site for information that's required to show your properties on the Jomres Super Server.","version":"0.2","description":"Allows the superserver to query the site for information that's required to show your properties on the Jomres Super Server.","author":"Vince Wooll","authoremail":"sales@jomres.net","lastupdate":"2018\/03\/14","min_jomres_ver":"9.10.0","manual_link":"","change_log":"v0.2 Adjustment to remove Jomres version from its old setting. ","highlight":"","image":"","demo_url":""},"api_feature_tariffs":{"name":"api_feature_tariffs","category":"REST API","marketing":"Functionality that allows